metadata.name: Water Pass #1
metadata.description: The Water Club is a collection of 6996 unique and dynamic membership passes living on the Ethereum blockchain. Each Water Club pass can be redeemed in the Ape Cave on www.apebeverages.com for 6 free cases of limited edition Ape Water delivered to your door over a period of 3 months.
